query:
SELECT 
  id,
  userId,
  domain,
  domainPrice,
  managementFee,
  totalPrice,
  status,
  stripePaymentIntentId,
  registrarOrderId,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt
FROM domain_orders
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
